            <p class="pub-card-text">Link material certificates, test reports, and supplier data to every lot. Trace any finished part back to its source material for compliance and quality investigations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pub-card pub-fade-up">
            <div class="pub-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="pub-card-title">Stock Locations</h3>
            <p class="pub-card-text">Manage inventory across multiple storage locations, shelves, and bins. Know exactly where every material lot is stored and track movements between locations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pub-card pub-fade-up">
            <div class="pub-card-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
                </svg>
